 Hitlers Younger Years.

I dont know if any of you have heard of this. But a series starring Robert Carlisle was recently cancelled because of the envovlment of a US Jewish organisation. The series was going to look at what Hitler was like in his childhood through is teens and his combat in WWI. There main complaint was that this series would 'humanise' the man.

I think this is bollocks. How can these people just have a TV company shut down a production just because they dont want people to see what the man was really like before all the Nazi stuff. They dont want there children to see what this guy was actually alike underneath all the Allied propaganda. Im not saying he was'nt a lunatic he was i know it ive seen all the old 9mm reels that soldiers took when the liberated such internment camps.

I think this needs a little debating.
